original_title: Freshmen Issue #91 Scene 2: Helmut Huxley and Jason Bacall
overview: Helmut is trying to explain to Jason the foundation of his relationship with Jerome while they’re enjoying a plate of meat and fries. He’s having a challenging time. The words “understanding”, “Friendly” and “Open” occur often. Since actions speak louder than words, Helmut decides that fucking Jason’s brains out would provide the best clarification. Justin’s satisfied smile at the end of Helmut’s “demonstration” indicates that he fully understands.
title: Freshmen Issue #91 Scene 2: Helmut Huxley and Jason Bacall
